<li id="cite_note-better-subsampling-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-better-subsampling_5-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFChan">Chan, Glenn. <a href="http://www.glennchan.info/articles/technical/chroma/chroma1.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.glennchan.info/articles/technical/chroma/chroma1.htm" rel="nofollow">"Towards Better Chroma Subsampling"</a>. <i><a href="http://www.glennchan.info/articles/technical/chroma/chroma1.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.glennchan.info/articles/technical/chroma/chroma1.htm" rel="nofollow">SMPTE Journal</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.glennchan.info/articles/technical/chroma/chroma1.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.glennchan.info/articles/technical/chroma/chroma1.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.glennchan.info/articles/technical/chroma/chroma1.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-08-29</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Towards+Better+Chroma+Subsampling&amp;rft.atitle=%5Bhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.glennchan.info%2Farticles%2Ftechnical%2Fchroma%2Fchroma1.htm+SMPTE+Journal%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Chan&amp;rft.aufirst=Glenn&amp;rft.au=Chan%2C+Glenn&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.glennchan.info%2Farticles%2Ftechnical%2Fchroma%2Fchroma1.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Chroma_subsampling"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ol>
</div>
<ul>
<li>Poynton, Charles. "YUV and <i>luminance</i> considered harmful: A plea for precise terminology in video" <a href="http://www.poynton.com/papers/YUV_and_luminance_harmful.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.poynton.com/papers/YUV_and_luminance_harmful.html" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
<li>Poynton, Charles. "Digital Video and HDTV: Algorithms and Interfaces." USA: Morgan Kaufmann Publishers, 2003.</li>
<li>Kerr, Douglas A. "Chrominance Subsampling in Digital Images" <a href="http://doug.kerr.home.att.net/pumpkin/Subsampling.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://doug.kerr.home.att.net/pumpkin/Subsampling.pdf" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></li>
</ul>
